item.title: Naga Rebel Accused in Ambush of Assam Rifles CO Viplav Tripathi and Others Arrested
item.description: Naga Rebel Accused in Ambush of Assam Rifles CO Viplav Tripathi and Others Arrested Accused was arrested and taken under custody for the ambush of Commanding Officer Viplav Tripathi with his family and four other personnel
